      header.separator
        //- h2
        //-   | Foo bar
      .row
        .4u#blog
          section
            a.image.feature(href='#')
              img(src='images/pic01.jpg', alt='')
            header
              h3 Blog
            p
              | Random ramblings on technology, computers, products, the Internet of Things and other cool stuff.
              | DIY solutions for home improvement, maintenance, redecorating, repair, renovation, and more.
              | A log of dietary intakes, home-grown produce, recipes, brewing coffee and beer.
