              a.button(href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/juan_paulo/' target='_blank')
                span.icon.fa-camera
                span &nbsp;Flickr page
        .4u#projects
          section
            a.image.feature.clip(href='#')
              img(src='images/pic02.jpg', alt='')
            header
              h3 Projects
            p
              | As an advocate of&nbsp;
              a(href='http://sloanreview.mit.edu/article/recapturing-monozukuri-in-toyotas-manufacturing-ethos/' target='_blank') Monozukuri
              |, I‘m consistently engaged in making things through various projects including Open Source Software, Activity Tracking, Data Visualization, Home Automation, Horticulture and Community Building. Check out the project page for more information!
